title: Mina's Medium Board
description:
Mina talks to Brandon Thorn of the Trench Warfare Newsletter about the top offensive and defensive linemen in the draft. Then ESPN's Jordan Reid joins to discuss the top RBs, TEs, LBs, CBs, and safeties.
